<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-32-0062 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper surveys the latest position of computer applications in chemistryin a number of educational, research and industrial institutions. Italso gives data on the computer facilities, computer time used by thechemistry departments and their opinion on the need of super-computersfor chemical applications in India.</TEXT></DOC>